messages.message:
Hey Brian,

Thank you for connecting with me! 

Just to break the ice, and give a quick intro...

I am a real estate investor, just like you. I'm one of the founding partners of a very unique turnkey investment company. We've been able to achieve some pretty incredible results by doing things a little differently,

Here is a quick 2 minute example of the kinds of off-market properties we make available to investors... 

https://youtu.be/cvwOKGv5Wc4

If you'd like to get returns like these, let me know... I'll be happy to send you more information.

To your success,

Shecky
